-- MOVES-Charles Hopkinson Woolley joins NewSmith from Tyrus Capital
-- 
-- Fri Oct 03, 2014 06:03AM EDT
-- None



Oct 3 (Reuters) - London-based specialist asset management firm NewSmith LLP said it appointed Charles Hopkinson Woolley the head of alternatives and product.

Woolley will guide the company's alternative investment strategies for investors in Europe, the United States and Japan, NewSmith said in a statement.